comments: Gobert's (UTA) slightly turns his body and initiates marginal contact to Wood's (DET) body during Wood's (DET) driving shot attempt.
Gobert (UTA) makes contact to McRae's (DET) arm after the release of the ball that affects his ability to follow through naturally.
Snell (DET) places a hand/arm to Bogdanovic's (UTA) front during the drive however, Bogdanovic (UTA) is able move through the marginal contact and continue along his desired path.
Mykhailiuk (DET) cleanly deflects the ball away from Gobert (UTA) as he attempts to retrieve the pass.
Mitchell (UTA) maintains a legal guarding position during Knight's (DET) jump shot attempt.
Wood (DET) is in the paint for longer than three seconds without actively guarding an opponent.
Mitchell (UTA) maintains a legal guarding position along McRae's (DET) path during his driving shot attempt.
Knight (DET) maintains a legal guarding position as Mitchell (UTA) loses control of the ball and dives for the loose ball. During the loose ball, both players mutually engage in marginal arm contact.
Wood (DET) makes contact to Gobert's (UTA) arm that affects his FOM.
Mykhailiuk (DET) commits a take foul on Mitchell (UTA).
Knight (DET) commits a take foul on Mitchell (UTA).
